        <TR>which is imperishable Niṣkala Śiva that manifests competely
            when one reaches the other shore of existence.</TR>
% for all sects?

<TEXT> sa śivaḥ sa paro brahmā sa viṣṇuḥ sa paro 'kṣaraḥ|</TEXT>
        <TR>It is Śiva, highest Brahmā, highest and imperishable Viṣṇu.</TR>

<TEXT> sa sūkṣmaḥ sa paro haṃsaḥ so 'kṣaraḥ kṣaravarjitaḥ||</TEXT> 20:88
