        <TR>What self-control, what tranquillity! What a sacrifice, what penance!</TR>
%folioinfo \msNa\ 231.jpg lower image

<TEXT> anenāmṛtavākyena vismayo me paro gataḥ|</TEXT>
        <APP>\vb <LEM>me paro gataḥ</LEM> \mssCaCbCc\msNa\msNc\Ed; \lac5 ××××× \msNb</APP>
